raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
do Story.mabel_kissed(\"Player\")
do Story.mabel_groped(\"Player\")
Mabel: Babe? You still on the bus home?
Player: Yep!
if Story.has_flag(\"AlcoholAcquired\"):
	Mabel: My head is aching
	Mabel: Am I supposed to drink water or not?
	- I think so
		Player: I think so
		Mabel: Okay I'll try
	- I don't know either lol
		Player: I don't know either lol
		Mabel: I should look it up then aaahh
	Mabel: We're totally never drinking again
	- I agree lol
		Player: I agree lol
		Mabel: How do people do this every weekend omg
	- Come on, you had fun
		Player: Come on, you had fun
		Mabel: BABE BARFING IS *NOTT* FUN
		Mabel: DOUBLE T, NOTT
		Player: Haha 😆
	Mabel: Anyway, apart from that little mess that was totally my fault
else:
	Mabel: I'm glad I got to watch some movies snuggled up with you hehe
	Mabel: Just like back home
	Mabel: I really missed doing that with you
	Mabel: I almost felt like it was never gonna happen again
	Player: Why?
	Mabel: I don't know... Just needed a familiar smell for a change
	Player: Is that why your nose was buried in my chest the whole time??
	Mabel: No way, it was not
	Player: Was too!
	Mabel: Was... okay maybe just a little
	Mabel: My dorm always smells crazy though!!
	Mabel: PinkThought: And your smell reminds me of home at least
	Player: Fair enough 😊
Mabel: Did you have a good time??
Mabel: I mean.. y'know...
if Story.has_flag(\"AlcoholAcquired\"):
	Mabel: Even though I went all kablooey! 🤮
	Player: You did go kablooey 😆
	Mabel: That felt so horrible 🙄
	Mabel: We're so never doing that again
	- Maybe we shouldn't
		Player: Maybe we shouldn't
		Mabel: Thank you!
	- Maybe we should
		Player: Maybe we should
		Mabel: We're so gonna argue about this later on 😣
	Player: It was a lot of fun though!
	Mabel: REALLY?
	Mabel: I mean 🙃
	Mabel: Did you really?
	Player: I really did!
else:
	Mabel: Doing that kind of thing with me?
	Player: I did
Mabel: You totally took pictures too omg
Player: I did that too 😁
Player: Hey it's good memories 😌
Mabel: 😭
Player: img: mabel/151
Mabel: Oh.. just this huh? 😇
Mabel: Did you like that movie?
Player: Time traveling dragon? 🤔
Player: I thought it was okay.. 👀
Mabel: It was so terrible LOL
Player: 😆
Mabel: Idk how it got high reviews 😂
Mabel: Phew, but that's all there was huh? 😅
Player: Plenty more 😈
Mabel: Oh nooo! 🙈
Player: Oh yesss
if Story.has_flag(\"AlcoholAcquired\"):
	Player: img: mabel/152
	Mabel: Oh no, can we forget about this part??? 😶
	Player: What do you mean? 😆
	Player: This was part of the experience
	Mabel: Omg meanie 🥺
	Mabel: It was my first time!!
	Player: Me too haha
	Mabel: Wow really?
	Mabel: It was like you weren't even affected by it 😳
	Player: No idea lol
	Player: img: mabel/153
	Mabel: Jeez that was a terrible feeling 🤢
	Mabel: My mouth was so stinky and I felt so ugly 😭
	Mabel: Thought: I hope you weren't grossed out by me babe
	Player: You're good lol
	Player: img: mabel/154
	Mabel: But I'd do it again if you hugged me like that 👀
	Player: No you wouldn't 😆
	Player: You were suffering a little too much
	Mabel: Well, I'd rather suffer all wrapped up with you 🤭
	Mabel: Thought: I'd totally pretend I was sick next time hehe
	Mabel: 🥰
	Player: 😏
else:
	Player: Like this one
	Player: img: mabel/155
	Mabel: omg
	Mabel: Are we getting better at it? 😳🫠
	Mabel: Thought: All the girls I see in my dorm kiss like that..
	Mabel: Thought: So I watched a few videos on it before you arrived...
	- It was surprising
		Player: It was surprising
		Mabel: Really? 👉👈
		Mabel: Maybe I should have said something before just suddenly doing it 🙈
	- You're really good at it
		Player: You're really good at it
		Mabel: Am I really? 🫠
		Player: Yeah! Sure you have no experience? 😏
		Mabel: Eep no! Cross my heart!!
		Mabel: Thought: That's a little scary to think
	Mabel: I'm glad it went well
Mabel: Actually I wanted to ask you for something 😶
Player: What's with that expression? 😆
Mabel: Remember when I uhm.. wanted to see you without your shirt on? 🙈
do heart(1)
Player: How could I forget 😉
Mabel: Well... I just wanted to have a picture of that on my phone..
- Of course!
	Player: Of course!
	Mabel: Yay 🥳
	Mabel: Thought: Thank god he's not teasing me about this
- How badly do you want it?
	Player: How badly do you want it?
	Mabel: 🙈
	Mabel: Badly, pretty pleaaase
Player: Here it is haha
Player: img: mabel/156
Mabel: 😍😍😍
Mabel: PinkThought: Goosebumpss!!!
Player: You really wanted it off 😄
Mabel: I'm just a girl with girl thoughts gee 😇
Mabel: I just wanted a little peek 🙈
Mabel: 👉👈
Mabel: Thanks ☺️
Player: Was it any good?
Mabel: It was perfect 🥰
Mabel: My hands were literally shaking did you notice?? 😭
Player: I did, was cute as heck!
Mabel: CUTE?? I didn't come off as a nervous wreck? 😣
do heart(1)
Mabel: Anyway!!
Player: Aren't you forgetting something?
Mabel: No idea what you're talking about 🥸
Player: Sure?
Mabel: Wait don't tell me you took a picture of that too 😶
do heart(1)
- Maybe ☺️
	Player: Maybe ☺️
- There might be a picture 👀
	Player: There might be a picture 👀
do heart(2)
Mabel: I... Wha
Mabel: 🥴
Player: Are you okay? 😆
Mabel: Apart from my heart about to blow out of my chest?... 🫠
Mabel: Totally fine! 👍👍
Player: I can delete it if you want
Mabel: Show me first 🙈
Mabel: Thought: I want to see if.. If I looked good for you
Player: img: mabel/157
Mabel: 😳
Mabel: Well, what did you think? 🙈
- You looked amazing
	Player: You looked amazing
- Nothing comes close to my babe
	Player: Nothing comes close to my babe
	do heart(3)
	Mabel: PinkThought: KYAAAAAAAAAAAA
	Mabel: Oh, okay 🙃
	Mabel: If you say so 🥰
	if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\"):
		Mabel: Thought: Take that Naomi!
Mabel: Okay then...
Player: img: mabel/158
Mabel: There was another picture? 😵
Player: Yeah 😁❤️
do heart(1)
do echo_set([\"159\"])
Mabel: PinkThought: My face... I remember that feeling
Mabel: PinkThought: Ugh I wish he could touch me like that every night
Mabel: PinkThought: It made me feel hot and squirmy
if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\"):
	Mabel: Thought: If I make him delete them then.. he won't be able to look at them after doing the shoot with Naomi...
Mabel: I guess you could keep the pictures 😶 ...if you want
Player: Wow really?
Mabel: Sure, but don't stare at them too much 🙈
Player: No promises!
if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\"):
	Mabel: Thought: You can stare at them as much as you want if you don't stare at Naomi's
do echo_clear()
Mabel: Boys 🙄
Player: 😇
do heart(0)
Mabel: Jeez ☺️
Mabel: If you wanted to do something like that again
Mabel: Just say so and... maybe we can
Mabel: If I have time 😊 I'm a busy girl!
Player: Sounds good 😍
Mabel: It was so nice that you slept over too 🥰
Mabel: Can you sleep over here from now on?
Player: And give up my classes?
Player: Absolutely!
Mabel: 😍
Mabel: It's okay, I'll work double hard for you! ☺️
Player: Bus is pulling over
Mabel: Make sure you eat something!!
Mabel: You didn't stay for breakfast 😭
Player: I will!
if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\"):
	Mabel: Behave with Naomi okay!? 😗
	Player: Okay! 🫡
Mabel: Okay, good
Mabel: And remember that I love you 😘
Player: I love you too! 😍
=> END"
